				<td width="150" height="25" valign="top"><span class="sub">Site Options:</span></td>
				<td>
					The  Site Elements form allows you to change the site-specific details such as titles, welcome message, header and footer sections. They include:<br><br>
					
					The URL of the site<br>
					The Titlte of the site<br>
					The Slogan of the site<br>
					The Title of the frontpage welcome message of the site<br>
					The Text of the frontpage welcome message of the site<br>
					The Organisation Name, URL, contact details and disclaimer link<br><br>
					
					To update these details simply type them and then press the Update button
				</td>
			</tr>
			
			<tr height="5"><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td></tr>
		</table>
		
		<a name="grap"></a>
