			<tr>
				<td width="150" height="25" valign="top"><span class="sub">Site Graphics:</span></td>
				<td>
					The  Site Graphics form allows you to update the number of graphics used in the web site. They include<br><br>
					
					The number of frontpage graphics<br>
					The number of banner graphics<br>
					The number of left graphics for main page (per category)<br>
					The number of right graphics for main page (per category)<br><br>
						
					To update these details simply type them and then press the Update button
				</td>
			</tr>
			
